org.locationtech.geowave.adapter.vector.plugin

Class GeoWaveGTDataStoreFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.adapter.vector.plugin.GeoWaveGTDataStoreFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.geotools.data.DataAccessFactory, org.geotools.data.DataStoreFactorySpi, org.geotools.util.factory.Factory

    public class GeoWaveGTDataStoreFactory
extends Object
implements org.geotools.data.DataStoreFactorySpi
    This factory is injected by GeoTools using Java SPI and is used to expose GeoWave as a DataStore to GeoTools. It should be defined within a file META-INF/services/org.geotools.data.DataStoreFactorySpi to inject this into GeoTools.
